About:
	My .bash git repository.

Installation:
	git clone git://github.com/Mrs-Rev/dotbash.git ~/.bash

Remove these files:

	cd ~
	rm .bashrc
	rm .bash_profile
	rm .profile

Create symlinks:

	cd ~
	ln -s .bash/.bashrc .bashrc 
	ln -s .bash/.bash_profile .bashrc_profile
	ln -s .bash/.profile .profile

